{"id":"e05ef23d-e0b2-4701-85b1-703a87ec4532","name":"“The Ones Who Betrayed You Are Back”","description":"<p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/uRoC5WWfZLYhBq7DoHD2o.webp\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>UPDATED: REMOVE STAIR LIKE FORMATTING</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 0);\"><strong>You were not defeated. You were not killed. You were inconvenient.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 0);\"><strong><em>Twenty years ago, the world of Aetheria chose victory over truth.</em></strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 0);\"><strong><em>They called it peace.</em></strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 0);\"><strong><em>They called it justice.</em></strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 0);\"><strong><em>They called you a monster.</em></strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 0);\"><strong><em>They lied.</em></strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>---</em></strong></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: c