: rgb(0, 255, 135);\"><strong><em>More control.</em></strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 135);\"><strong><em>So they started a war—and told the world the demons did.</em></strong></span></p><p c","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"kzmxNgxJplty0jQ3FtT2m.webp","creator":"Dia_blo","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","📚 Fictional","🎲 RPG","👤 AnyPOV","💔 Angst","❤️‍🔥 Smut","🌗 Switch"],"chats":4257,"messages":54989,"created_at":"2026-04-16T13:00:51.378604+00:00"}